ABILITIES: Racial and OCC special abilities

Syntax: abilities

DESCRIPTION:
  Shows your racial special abilities, racial penalties, and OCC-granted
  abilities for Rifts characters.

  The display includes:
    - Racial abilities and penalties
    - OCC description, type flags, and base skills
    - Current APM (attacks per melee)
    - PPE and ISP pools when applicable

NOTES:
  Non-Rifts races see a short message instead of a full list.
  Use score for combat stats and skills for trained skill levels.

SEE ALSO: score, skills, stats, psionics
